catList: The structures of the universe in order of increasing distance from the solar system: the sun and the planets. Stars and star clusters. Galaxies and galaxy clusters. The Hubble Law. The cosmic microwave background. Cosmology. How does a star shine - stellar structure and evolution. Endpoints of stellar evolution - black holes, white dwarfs and neutron stars. Methods of observation across the electromagnetic spectrum. Satellite observatories and space research.
